aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Ksmien Men's Running Shorts 7 Inch with Zipper Pockets Quick Dry Lightweight Athletic Shorts for Workout Gym Basketball 
The men's running shorts by Ksmien combining comfort, great fit and versatility was designed for the sport-loving man. These mens athletic shorts, come equipped with secure pockets and lightweight fabric to keep up with your daily agenda.They are featured with lightweight, quick dry, breathable, water resistant fabric and UPF 50+ sun protection function, to provide great protection against harmful ultraviolet rays and keep you refreshing and breathable for your all-day comfort. 
3 Functional Pockets: Mens running shorts with 1 side deep zipper pocket provide safe storage for your phone, keys, cash, etc. 2 deep slash pockets for storage convenience, and keep you hands free. 
Adjustable Elastic Waistband: The mens shorts have a 360-degree elastic waist with adjustable drawstring to prevent pressure marks on the tummy and offers a custom fit during running or workout. 
Split Hem Design: Side splits at hem for ventilated comfort and freedom to move. These athletic workout shorts for men have a split hem to keep you agile. 
Breathable & Quick dry fabric: Highly breathable fabric lets moisture out, making sure you stay dry on the inside. 
Water Resistant: Moisture-wicking fabric is treated with a durable water repellent (DWR) to shed light rain and stains. 
Reflective Logo: Reflective elements for increased visibility during low light situations. 
Sun Protection: UPF 50+ Sun Protection, helping to protect your skin from the sun's harmful rays.
